Mpcnetwork testnet is about optimizing older hardware with newer hardware. utilizing what they do to offload processorpower from the newer systems when possible. 
The computer age is well on it's way. continious innovations will bring out more capable , more ... hardware. The older hardware that was the pinnacle of innovation mere years earlier is becoming discarded.
but that is amazing hardware. it's quit incomprehensible. Ai optimizing utilization of different architectures. 
the digitalization will increasingly provide us with an array of systems. many dislocated, non addressable older hardware. 
Smart connections, take older hardware, sit inbetween the hardware and the rest of the infrastructure is an addressable ai switch. The switch is the smart device , other hardware can connect to.
